comments: Gordon (ORL) and Galloway (DET) simultaneously come together during the rebound.
After gathering the ball on the rebound, Gordon (ORL) releases the pass prior re-landing on his pivot foot.
Vucevic (ORL) has a stayed hand on Morris' (DET) back and does not dislodge him during the rebound.
During the pick, Carter-Williams (ORL) holds Wood (DET) and affects his FOM.
Maker (DET) makes contact to Fultz's (ORL) arm during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Fultz (ORL) makes clean contact to the ball and avoids making contact to Maker's (DET) arm on the follow-through during the shot attempt.
Vucevic (ORL) makes marginal contact to Maker's (DET) body during his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Wood (DET) touched the ball while it is outside of the imaginary cylinder above the rim.
Vucevic (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Snell (DET) and absorbs the contact.
Jackson (DET) slightly extends his arms into Carter-Williams (ORL) during the screen.
Fultz (ORL) makes incidental contact to Galloway's (DET) arm after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Fournier (ORL) slightly extends his arm into Galloway (DET) on the perimeter.
Vucevic (ORL) briefly grasps Galloway's (DET) jersey in the post off-ball.
Vucevic (ORL) is not in the path of Snell (DET) when he sets the screen but the contact is marginal.
Vucevic (ORL) engage and disengages with Wood (DET) during the rebound.
Vucevic (ORL) makes clean contact to the ball while defending the incoming pass to Wood (DET).
Galloway (DET) commits a take foul on Fournier (ORL).
Snell (DET) commits a take foul on Fournier (ORL).
Fournier (ORL) brushes Jackson's (DET) arm during the rebound.
Jackson (DET) commits a take foul on Fultz (ORL).
